{"docs":{"name":"Dynamica","info":"Another API description","copyright":null,"doc_url":"../../apidocs/v1","api_url":"/api","resources":[{"doc_url":"../../apidocs/v1/forecasts","api_url":"/api","name":"Forecasts","short_description":null,"full_description":null,"version":"v1","formats":null,"metadata":null,"methods":[{"doc_url":"../../apidocs/v1/forecasts/index","name":"index","apis":[{"api_url":"/api/v1/projects/:project_id/forecasts","http_method":"GET","short_description":"List of all the project forecasts","deprecated":null}],"formats":null,"full_description":"\n\u003cp\u003eIt returns a list of all the forecasts creted in the project.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSuccessful request responds with 200 status code.\u003c/p\u003e\n","errors":[{"code":403,"description":"Access denied","metadata":null},{"code":500,"description":"Server error","metadata":null}],"params":[],"examples":["// GET /api/v1/projects/my-shop/forecasts\n\n// Response\n\n[\n  {\n    \"forecast\":{\n      \"id\":85,\n      \"period\":\"day\",\n      \"group_method\":\"sum\",\n      \"depth\":5,\n      \"from\":null,\n      \"to\":null,\n      \"planned_at\":\"2015-03-06T14:32:14.380Z\",\n      \"started_at\":null,\n      \"finished_at\":null,\n      \"workflow_state\":\"planned\"\n    }\n  },\n  {\n    \"forecast\":{\n      \"id\":86,\n      \"period\":\"day\",\n      \"group_method\":\"sum\",\n      \"depth\":5,\n      \"from\":null,\n      \"to\":null,\n      \"planned_at\":\"2015-03-06T14:32:14.383Z\",\n      \"started_at\":\"2015-03-06T14:33:14.093Z\",\n      \"finished_at\":\"2015-03-06T14:35:14.093Z\",\n      \"workflow_state\":\"finished\"\n    }\n  }\n]\n"],"metadata":null,"see":[]},{"doc_url":"../../apidocs/v1/forecasts/create","name":"create","apis":[{"api_url":"/api/v1/projects/:project_id/forecasts","http_method":"POST","short_description":"Create a forecast","deprecated":null}],"formats":null,"full_description":"\n\u003cp\u003eCreate a new forecast. New forecast will be created in “planned” state and will be planned to the closest available time.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSuccessful request responds with 201 status code. Otherwise see error codes list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"forecast_setup_examples\"\u003eForecast setup examples\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003col\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere is an online store. After each order it send to Dynamica data about just sold products (its SKU and sold quantity). Assume that we want to predict sales in next 2 month. What we need is to group previous purchases by month and sum them. So, the following request should be sent:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e{ \u0026quot;forecast\u0026quot;: { \u0026quot;period\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;month\u0026quot;, \u0026quot;depth\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;2\u0026quot;, \u0026quot;group_method\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;sum\u0026quot; } }\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEvery hour we send to Dynamica data about RUB to USD exchange rate. We want to predict the exchange for the next 5 days. Now there is not sense to calculate sum of all these values. We are interested in the average exchange rate for each day. So, the following request should be sent:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ccode\u003e{ \u0026quot;forecast\u0026quot;: { \u0026quot;period\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;day\u0026quot;, \u0026quot;depth\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;5\u0026quot;, \u0026quot;group_method\u0026quot;: \u0026quot;average\u0026quot; } }\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ol\u003e\n","errors":[{"code":422,"description":"Unprocessable entity","metadata":null},{"code":403,"description":"Access denied","metadata":null},{"code":500,"description":"Server error","metadata":null}],"params":[{"name":"forecast","full_name":"forecast","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eDescription of a new forecast\u003c/p\u003e\n","required":true,"allow_nil":false,"validator":"Must be a Hash","expected_type":"hash","metadata":null,"show":true,"params":[{"name":"period","full_name":"forecast[period]","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eTime unit of the forecast.\u003c/p\u003e\n","required":true,"allow_nil":false,"validator":"Must be one of: day, month.","expected_type":"string","metadata":null,"show":true},{"name":"depth","full_name":"forecast[depth]","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eDepth of the forecast in selected time units. Default: 14 days or 2 month\u003c/p\u003e\n","required":false,"allow_nil":false,"validator":"Must be Integer","expected_type":"numeric","metadata":null,"show":true},{"name":"group_method","full_name":"forecast[group_method]","description":"\n\u003cp\u003eHow to group values on. Default: “sum”\u003c/p\u003e\n","required":false,"allow_nil":false,"validator":"Must be one of: sum, average.","expected_type":"string","metadata":null,"show":true}]}],"examples":["// POST /api/v1/projects/my-shop/forecasts\n\n{ \"forecast\": { \"period\": \"month\", \"depth\": \"2\", \"group_method\": \"sum\" } }\n\n// Response\n\n{\n  \"forecast\":{\n    \"id\":88,\n    \"period\":\"month\",\n    \"depth\":2,\n    \"group_method\":\"sum\",\n    \"from\":null,\n    \"to\":null,\n    \"workflow_state\":\"planned\",\n    \"planned_at\":\"2015-03-06T15:16:58.420Z\"\n  }\n}\n"],"metadata":null,"see":[]}]}],"link_extension":".html"}}